data.description: Discover serenity in this charming Bella Vista home, surrounded by a beautiful view of lush green trees. The living room boasts coffered ceilings, wood floors, and a cozy fireplace. A spacious kitchen offers ample cabinet space, granite counter tops, and brand new appliances. Roomy closets offer desirable storage space, along with a convenient laundry area. Step outside to find a large covered deck and spacious fenced backyard for outdoor enjoyment, and a stunning brick front exterior. You'll make delightful memories here for years to come.
